Package: Chloris
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Framework for Copy Number Alteration Analysis in scRNA-seq
Version: 0.1.1
Author: Puxue Qiao
Maintainer: Puxue Qiao <pqiao@svi.edu.au>
Description: Chloris provides a Bayesian framework for analysing intra-tumoral heterogeneity of copy number alterations (CNA) from single-cell RNA sequencing data. It enables identification of clonal structure and integrates BAF and RDR information for robust inference.
